<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{وَمِنْهُم من يَسْتَمِعُون إِلَيْك}</span> يَعْنِي: جَمَاعَةً يَسْتَمِعُونَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{أَفَأَنْتَ تُسْمِعُ الصُّمَّ وَلَوْ كَانُوا لَا يَعْقِلُونَ}</span> وَهَذَا سمع الْقبُول.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>سُورَة يُونُس من الْآيَة <span class="c2">(٤٣)</span> إِلَى الْآيَة <span class="c2">(٥٢)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>